          <head type="note" n="1" xml:id="spp-432ACWJS-headnote-1">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-432ACWJS-headnote-1-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-432ACWJS-headnote-1-line-group-1-line-1">By M<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> L──────. Sept<hi rend="superscript">br</hi> 7<hi rend="superscript">th</hi> 1728.</l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <head type="note" n="2" xml:id="spp-432ACWJS-headnote-2">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-432ACWJS-headnote-2-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-432ACWJS-headnote-2-line-group-1-line-1"></l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <head type="note" n="3" xml:id="spp-432ACWJS-headnote-3">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-432ACWJS-headnote-3-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-432ACWJS-headnote-3-line-group-1-line-1"></l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <lg n="1">
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-432ACWJS-line-1" n="1">A slave to crowds, scortch't with the summers heats,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-432ACWJS-line-2" n="2">In Court the wretched Lawyer toyls and sweats</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-432ACWJS-line-3" n="3">While smiling Nature in her best attire</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-432ACWJS-line-4" n="4">Does sooth each sense and vernal joy inspire.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-432ACWJS-line-5" n="5">Can he, who knows that real good should please</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-432ACWJS-line-6" n="6">Barter for gold his Liberty and Ease?</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-432ACWJS-line-7" n="7"><lb/>Thus Paulus preach'd: When entring at the door</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-432ACWJS-line-8" n="8">Upon his board a Clyent pours the ore:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-432ACWJS-line-9" n="9">He grasps the shining gift, pores o'er the Cause,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-432ACWJS-line-10" n="10">Forgets the Sun, and dozes on the Laws.</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
      </div>
